parameters: What happened, Lunaroa-chan? Um, did you two break up...?

Kyaa♡ Lunaroa-chan♡!... Tch. If only this person wasn't
here...

Welcome... You have come here often. This is the deepest
part of the Trial of Ice....

You are the chosen one... right? Could you come over here
for a moment...? May I have a look at your face...?

Ahh ♡ So cute!! Your face has a lingering youthfulness and
long, mature hair.... I can't help but feel all fluttery,
big sister...!

You... are very strong, aren't you? You know, I really like
to properly train girls like you and turn them into my
slaves....

At first, you seem frustrated... but in the end, you'll be
begging on your own... The contrast is irresistible... ♡

Hey, won't you become my slave...? Don't worry... there's
nothing to be afraid of. You won't be able to live without
me soon... ♡

\SE[60]I mean, it's just a misunderstanding!! \SE[100]My
Lunaroa is the strongest childhood friend that can't be
beaten by anyone...!!
Hey... what are you doing? Don't touch my lover, okay?

\SE[123]Th... This...!! Lover!!! \SE[102]I can't believe
this amateur...!!
So, what are you to this girl?

\SE[102]I am Lunaroa's lover!! If she wishes, I can even
become her slave!! \SE[40]That's why! To you!! There are no
boundaries!!!
\SE[11] (Yay. I got her to give me her word.)

Hmmm? Is that so? Well then, if you were to disappear, it
means that anything that gets in my way will vanish, right?

\SE[102]What makes you think... that I would be defeated by
someone like you...!!
I will make this insignificant little girl disappear...!

\SE[102]Bring it on...! \!\SE[40]Come at me, you old
hag...!!
